data.description: Welcome to this stunning Dutch colonial style home. With 5 beds and 2.5 baths, this home offers ample space for you and your loved ones to create unforgettable memories. As you make your way through the main level, you'll appreciate the freshly painted interior and the LVP flooring that flows seamlessly from room to room. The beautiful kitchen features granite countertops and upgraded black stainless-steel appliances. With plenty of storage and counter space, meal preparation becomes a breeze. Imagine unwinding in the den in front of the wood burning fireplace, where an expansive window offers stunning views of the water and woods. Upstairs, you'll discover a spacious owner’s suite that is truly a retreat with an upgraded walk-in shower, creating a spa-like experience right in the comfort of your own home. You'll love spending time on the enclosed porch, great for simply enjoying a quiet morning coffee while taking in the picturesque surroundings. Schedule your private tour today!
